    "name": "风与鸟 - Wind and Bird",
    "steam_appid": 2269860,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/629d4c48d2601aaee361b9d7a73714ba.avif?t=1726659549\" width=614 height=200 /></span><br>《风与鸟》是一款奇幻题材、横版剧情向rpg游戏。<br>内容以剧情演出为主，也有选项和简单的qte要素穿插在游戏流程中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/3ae55d2cfb0420ad441f5bac6b7befc6.avif?t=1726659549\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br>长耳族的吟游诗人学徒蒂娜正在跟随着成熟的导师基德进行着周游大陆的探寻之旅。但在一场酒馆演出中，蒂娜却表现出了相当青涩的演出水平。<br>震惊的师父开始反思自己的教育方针，并决定对蒂娜进行吟游诗人特训！<br>刚成为学徒不久的蒂娜就要面对谜语人师父设下的重重考验，她能否顺利成长为合格的吟游诗人？<br><br>经历一路的风景和人文体验，蒂娜游历了充满故事的高塔小镇、穿过了矗立巨石的青色草原，心中的故事页数也在逐渐增加，脱笼的鸟儿正要展翅翱翔。<br>然而成长之旅绝非一帆风顺。<br>不平凡的旅途开头，也将对应着不一般的旅途结尾……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/0a86b18ee6c276aa61030203eac43ea4.avif?t=1726659549\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/4ff1b83aff40d364e7224c4b15312b00.avif?t=1726659549\" width=144 height=209 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蒂娜</h2>青涩的吟游诗人学徒，跟随师父修行中。<br>不善交流，但在一点点地学习。<br>『师父，教教我——』<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/c7a63606c7c995d30e73f9f7b28b078e.avif?t=1726659549\" width=144 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >师父</h2>成熟的吟游诗人大师，精通演出与讲故事。<br>平日开朗健谈，偶尔也会脱线。<br>『故事就在你眼前。去吧，蒂娜。』<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/4df96ca7f0d3113872447f8f5dd7984d.avif?t=1726659549\" width=144 height=211 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >艾莉娜</h2>高塔之城的新晋管理者，隶属于务实的大地一派。<br>年纪轻轻便肩负重任。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/63ae66f5ff0627d207da1d90864db4ed.avif?t=1726659549\" width=144 height=209 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >春菊</h2>路过的活泼吟游诗人。<br>将吟游诗人大师「蒲公英」视为偶像。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/4e3e5ae6231c1e19eea79ce38c998a29.avif?t=1726659549\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有趣的剧情-观察师徒演出前后的趣味对话，陪伴蒂娜一起旅行，一同吐槽师父的奇思妙想。<br></li><li>清新的画面-游戏中的多个场景拥有令人舒适的吟游诗人主题色，贴近自然的森林绿和天空蓝。<br></li><li>优秀的音乐-故事全流程拥有精心挑选的音乐加持，参与叙事的曲子将给您留下深刻的印象。<br></li><li>巧妙的剧本-插叙与叙事主题的巧妙结合，将故事的全貌留到了最后一刻揭晓！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/31cc94d56e270cf5019cede7ff633392.avif?t=1726659549\" width=615 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「游戏时长」</h2>30分钟-60分钟<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「结局数量」</h2>单结局<br>通关后将在标题界面解锁特典房间<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「操作方式」</h2>方向键←→：进行移动<br><br>Z/空格/Enter：对话/调查物品<br>X/ESC：取消/打开菜单<br>Shift+←→： 跑步<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269860/extras/76b7512fdae8929679e5911d110a8cab.avif?t=1726659549\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br>制作人、剧本：摇曳铃<br>美术：芝秋白，ONE，百合子，雅弥，广廿尺，摇曳铃<br>UI协力：黛惠<br>发行：梦结界工作室",
